data.description: Amazing views at an affordable price! Sit on your deck and enjoy the beautiful sunset over Lake Winnebago. Some updates already done. Newer flooring, first floor laundry, stunning master bath to name a few. Enjoy your main floor master bedroom with en suite or use the large bedroom upstairs with attached 3 season room and enjoy the view while sipping wine by the electric fireplace. 2 additional bedrooms upstairs. Large kitchen/dining area are open to the main living area, all boasting a great view of the lake! Almost an acre to spread out and enjoy the treed lot. Partially fenced area for pets, kids, etc. Large basement has walkout door and a workshop area. Conveniently located, close enough to town but far enough away to be private.
